Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:07.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\NWithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:20.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:23.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:25.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:32.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:38.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:40.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:55.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:01:02.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:09.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\NWhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.53,0:01:12.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:18.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:25.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:28.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is…  Her Spiritual Pressure is\Ngoing out of control?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:42.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rantao! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can use this artifact
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to remove the spirit energy\Nthat's going out of control inside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:05.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've reached my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:13.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not safe here!\NLet's go somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can get away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You managed to escape death,\Nbut this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:31.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you’re in a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:50.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:05.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about me…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Rantao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:14.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, take Rantao and\Nget away from here…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:17.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm going to\Ntake on Kariya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like that's our only choice…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:22.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:31.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:52.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:08.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness…\NYou're safe…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What happened\Nto your artifact?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It broke…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:24.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it supposed to explode\Nif it broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… As I reached my limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:31.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I realized how to use the artifact\Nfor just amplifying reishi…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:36.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That way, it wouldn't explode\Nwhen I surpassed my limit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,because it was already empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:40.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter as long as he's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:46.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop going off on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:53.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:57.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are they there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:59.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:00.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ichigo Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's fighting Kariya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:14.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let Ichigo Kurosaki handle\Nthis burden on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:16.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:22.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:26.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… This is Rantao…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:30.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rantao?! The exiled engineer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She created the Bounts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:38.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Thirteen Court Guard\NSquads Captain, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:39.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to do something for me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:45.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Seireitei will be finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:48.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know that Kariya has\Nabsorbed the Jokai Crest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:54.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,into his body, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:58.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've already researched that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Jokai Crest is definitely powerful…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:05.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But he'll need time in order to\Nuse its full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:10.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he's probably\Nbuying himself time right now…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:17.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… But the Jokai Crest power\Nthat's in Kariya isn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a different power\Nwe need to worry about…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:21.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A different power?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“Jokai Crest” is the general term
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:28.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,for giant reishi-generating devices\Nwe used to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:32.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There were probably, at least,\Nseveral dozen within Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:37.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One day, a Jokai Crest went out\Nof control during an experiment…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:44.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When it exploded, it annihilated about\Na tenth of Seireitei…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:52.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The leaders at the time took this\Nvery seriously and sealed away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:55.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,all of the Jokai Crests that\Nwere in Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! There's more than one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:13.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If Kariya blows up the Jokai Crest\Nthat he's absorbed into his body…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It would probably set off\Nall the other Jokai Crests…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:21.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is Kariya's true goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:25.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If all of the Jokai Crests explode,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,their destructive force would\Nbe unfathomable…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:33.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are such things in Seireitei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because they're dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:39.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and dangerous things need\Nto be kept in sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…\N“People often know little of…”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:42.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"what's happening in\Ntheir own backyards,” right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:44.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:51.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to seal each\NJokai Crest with kido once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:56.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Many years have passed,\Nand their current seals have weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:59.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They'll react to Kariya's explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:00.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:03.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right… We'll arrange to have them\Nre-sealed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where\Nthe Jokai Crests are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:10.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here is…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rantao!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:16.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:21.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fighting with my Spiritual Pressure\Nsealed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:22.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm overextending myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:25.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've just reached the limit to\Nwhich I can be active…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:31.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I leave the rest to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:36.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:39.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What will you be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:40.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:43.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going after Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:49.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki is fighting.\NWe can't just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:54.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I've got to heal\NKurosaki's wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:55.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, let me carry Rantao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:03.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go once we've taken Rantao\Nsomewhere she can rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sado.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:10.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now that it's decided,\Nlet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally drawing towards\Nthe conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see this to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:16.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go after Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:35.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I commend you for keeping up\Nwith me this far…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:39.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to settle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:46.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what kind\Nof place this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:49.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Far better than you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:57.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This place is perfect\Nfor settling this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Flash and Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nijigasumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:26.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:50.60,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,SEIREITEI LIBRARY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rantao gave us this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a copy of a map that shows\Nwhere the Jokai Crest seals are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, my… After all that’s happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:00.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who would have thought that\Nthere was still such a thing left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:03.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that we stayed up\Nall night for nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:06.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Now's not the time\Nto be saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you told\Nthe General Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've sent Matsumoto to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We should get some orders soon…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:19.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case,\Nto seal this many Jokai Crests,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:22.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we need to mobilize all of\Nour remaining captains,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,lieutenants,\Nand high-ranking officers…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do about Kariya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki's gone after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:38.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captains, lieutenants,\Nand squad members of all ranks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of the Thirteen Court Guard Squads,\Nthis is an urgent report!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The ryoka are after an ancient item\Nknown as a Jokai Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:46.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've confirmed\Nthe existence of several.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:51.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Jokai Crests need to be\Nsealed away immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:54.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Issuing a level one\Nprecautionary warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is to head to\Na Jokai Crest seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We shall use hell butterflies\Nto lead you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Lieutenant Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:10.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go to a Jokai Crest seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:11.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:13.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Given the nature of the circumstances…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:16.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall directly lead everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:19.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Komamura, assist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:21.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:29.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the fight\Non Sokyoku Hill has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:29.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All of the Soul Reapers in Seireitei\Nhave been mobilized…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:36.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Ichigo Kurosaki\Nis the one fighting the ryoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:40.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We should start\Npreparing to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask Lord Byakuya\Nfor instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:43.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:08.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kariya…\NThere's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:10.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Koga and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:16.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Died?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:21.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… They all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:26.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:41.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:49.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said, “Stop!”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:02.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NYou're all worn out…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Ichinose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you told me\Nto destroy Seireitei,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:26.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would have no choice\Nbut to do so…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:29.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have abandoned this place…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My heart would not hurt\Nif it disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:33.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:42.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I saw my respected captain in you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:47.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I served by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:48.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:55.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to serve justice.\NWhy do you stand before us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:15:59.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:03.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:07.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Relying on people and loyalty\Nare different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:08.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk as if you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenpachi Zaraki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,During my battle with Zaraki,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:19.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered something\NI had forgotten…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to turn the Thirteen\NCourt Guard Squads…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:30.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seireitei into something even\Nslightly better than what it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was my wish…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:38.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My captain and I wanted\Nthe same world…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:42.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I worked my hardest\Nby my captain's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:46.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My ideal will not change\Neven if he is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:52.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But the emptiness of\Nmy captain's death
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:55.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,changed my desires into revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:01.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kariya…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:06.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've gained the power\Nto change Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:10.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall kneel before you once more
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:14.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if you will use your power\Nto rebuild Seireitei…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:17.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:23.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If…If you will only use it for revenge…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:26.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:30.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can be born of revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:35.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Koga and\Nthe other Bounts are dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:39.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the only one who can stop you\Nis me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kariya…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichinose…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:49.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:01.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop me with your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your help…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:13.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you've allowed me time for\Nthe Jokai Crest's power
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to spread through my body…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kari…ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:53.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:57.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard…\NDo you know what you just did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:59.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You killed your comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He served by your side…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:06.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:07.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“What about it”?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was your enemy…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you pity him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:17.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't pity him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm saying that\NI can't forgive you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:22.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,for killing your comrade\Nso coldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:27.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought of them\Nas comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:31.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They were pawns I used\Nto achieve my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:35.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:41.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to settle this\Nwith you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zeige Dih, Messer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What fierce wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:18.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I can sense Kariya's\NSpiritual Pressure rising rapidly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:19.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think there was\Na need to show you my doll…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:37.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems I'm almost out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:42.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is my doll, Messer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:46.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't come near me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:50.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've sure got confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:15.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:17.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:21.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find my captain,\Nso I came for him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:23.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:27.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:36.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the Sokyoku…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:41.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:15.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You always lament on\Nhow boring this town is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:19.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Searching for a place in the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:24.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The melody you hum is that\Nrusty, same old song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:28.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Rejecting any new song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:37.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're anxious because somewhere\Nin your heart, you believe in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:40.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's you;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:47.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That pain will eventually become\Na memory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:49.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:57.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think, just feel,\Nlet your whole body tremble;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:22:58.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,future is you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.16,0:23:01.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's me;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:08.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're never alone, I'm right here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:10.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We should be as one;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:14.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stumble, I don’t mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.19,0:23:20.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell you now\Nabout the thing called love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.60,0:23:24.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soon I'll be filled with\Nthe Jokai Crest's power
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:29.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and I will wipe Seireitei\Nfrom this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing anyone can\Ndo to stop me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:35.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya… I'll stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:37.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you destroy this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:49.26,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers\NGolden after these messages!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:51.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Illustrated guide to Soul Reapers!\N– Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:54.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:58.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Kurosaki and the others\Nshould be resting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:00.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone sure has it hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.88,0:24:03.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll use\Nmy soothing powers…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.28,0:24:05.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:06.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– The Substitute Soul Reaper has…\N– No…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.80,0:24:08.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– …begun fighting the Bount.\N– You can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.19,0:24:09.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Return to your command posts.\N– You can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.95,0:24:11.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– All right.\N– You can't touch that…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:12.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.88,0:24:16.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:17.75,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,SILENCE…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.48,0:24:18.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:27.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,R-Regretful…